1. *Nazovi* me kad završiš s poslom. (Call me when you finish the job.)
2. Ona ga je *nazvala* po imenu. (She called him by name.)
3. Obično *nazivam* ga bratom. (I usually call him brother.)
4. *Nazovite* me ako vam treba pomoć. (Call me if you need help.)
5. *Nazove* li on tebe? (Will he call you?)